voids.name: Silentium
voids.nature: A still point in the turning wheel. It neither gives nor takes, but holds.
voids.whisper: *"Silence. Stillness. The Altar awaits your offering."*

voids.name: Lethe Perpetua
voids.nature: The star of silence. Here, thought dissolves into primordial emptiness.
voids.whisper: *"I hold nothing. I am nothing. Yet without me, nothing stands."*

voids.name: Dumah
voids.nature: The star of silence. Here, thought dissolves into primordial emptiness.
voids.whisper: *"I hold nothing. I am nothing. Yet without me, nothing stands."*

voids.name: Samael Aeterna
voids.nature: A still point in the turning wheel. It neither gives nor takes, but holds.
voids.whisper: *"Sink into me. Release. The Void embraces all."*
